com.iver.cit.gvsig.fmap.rendering.IClassifiedLegend, com.iver.cit.gvsig.fmap.rendering.IClassifiedVectorLegend, com.iver.cit.gvsig.fmap.rendering.ILegend, com.iver.cit.gvsig.fmap.rendering.IVectorLegend, com.iver.utiles.IPersistence
public class VectorFilterExpressionLegend
extends com.iver.cit.gvsig.fmap.rendering.AbstractClassifiedVectorLegend

Implements a vectorial legend which represents the elements of a layer depending on the value of an expression. That is, if the expression is evaluated to true, then the symbol associated to the expression is painted. In other case it is not showed.

Author:
Pepe Vidal Salvador - jose.vidal.salvador@iver.es
